name: Silver Filigree Cab with Purple and Peach Floral Heart

This pretty ring is set on a silver filigree base which is fully adjustable. The band is approximately 15mm wide at it's widest point.

Set on the ring is an acrylic heart in purple with a peach floral centre. The heart is approximately 16mm in diameter.

name: Gunmetal and Dark Pink Sakura Floral Ring
description:
This simple floral ring is on a gunmetal plated adjustable band, so should fit most fingers.

The centrepiece is a resin rose coloured sakura flower.

The band is approximately 4mm wide at it's widest point.

The flower is approximately 12mm in diameter.

name: Round Purple Floral Limogue Ring
description:
This pretty and vintage inspired ring is set on an adjustable ring base, so should fit most fingers.

With an antique silver frame, the centrepiece is a lovely vintage West German floral cab which is approximately 25mm in diameter and is in the loveliest shade of lavender.

name: Silver Ring with Yellow & Orange Flower Tapestry Cab
description:
This lovely little ring is set on an antique silver plated adjustable band. The acrylic centrepiece has a floral motif with a raised dotted texture which makes it appear like its a tapestry.

As the ring is adjustable, it should fit most fingers.

The oval centrepiece is approximately 18mm x 13mm.

name: Gold Ring with Pink & Maroon Rose Cab
description:
This lovely little ring is set on a gold plated adjustable band and features a gold plated lace edging. The vintage inspired centrepiece is a picture of a maroon and pink rose with a delicate gold frame.

As the ring is adjustable, it should fit most fingers.

The oval centrepiece is approximately 18mm x 13mm.

name: Pink Filigree Ring with Pink Enameled Flower
description:
This pretty ring is set on an adjustable pink filigree band, so it should fit most fingers.

The focal piece of the ring is a enamel metal light pink large flower. The flower is approximately 25mm in diameter.

name: White Beaded Necklace with Bunny Pendant and Peach & Black Flowers
description:
This whimsical woodland piece is set on a white acrylic beaded chain and features a round charm with a picture of a bunny. It's accented with a black and coral coloured glass flower.

The chain is approximately 49cm long.

The round pendant with the rabbit is approximately 25mm in diameter.

name: Gold Necklace with Pink Lasercut Rose
description:
This lovely necklace is on a gold plated long rectangular link chain and has a pretty pink rose charm that has been laser cut from acrylic. The print of the flower is exquisite!

The chain is approximately 52cm long (20.47").
The flower is approximately 45mm x 35mm.

name: Silver Necklace with Mint and Black Girl and Bow
description:
This pretty necklace is on a silver plated fine ball chain and features a lovely pendant with a picture of a girl with long hair that has so many things in it, on a mint background. It's set in an antique silver frame that has a fancy lace edge. Hanging from this pendant is a pretty mint green enamelled bow.

The chain is approximately 50cm long.

The pendant is approximately 30mm x 23mm (excluding the bow).

name: Black Framed Steam Ship Necklace
description:
This necklace features a black resin frame with an acrylic centrepiece which has a picture of a steam ship. Hanging from the pendant is a silver plated helm. It has a black enamelled chain with several black beads around the pendant.

The pendant is approximately 50mm x 40mm.

The necklace is approximately 61cm long.

name: Antique Brass Babushka Matryoshka Necklace with Bar Chain - Blue, Red & Navy
description:
A pretty charm necklace with a babushka / matryoshka doll - whatever you want to call her! This necklace is on a pretty antique brass bar chain, that is really lovely. Hanging off it is an oval pendant with a picture of a babushka doll in blue, red and navy with a white background. 

The pendant is approximately 18mm x 13mm.

The chain is approximately 52cm long.

name: Antique Brass Babushka Matryoshka Necklace with Bar Chain - Red, Green & Purple
description:
A pretty charm necklace with a babushka / matryoshka doll - whatever you want to call her! This necklace is on a pretty antique brass bar chain, that is really lovely. Hanging off it is an oval pendant with a picture of a babushka doll in red, green and purple with a white background. 

The pendant is approximately 18mm x 13mm.

The chain is approximately 52cm long.

name: Pink Filigree Ring with Light Pink Flower
description:
This pretty ring is set on an adjustable pink filigree band, so it should fit most fingers.

The focal piece of the ring is a resin pale pink large flower. The flower is approximately 20mm in diameter.

name: Gold Ring with Grey & White Cab Flower
description:
This pretty little ring features a grey rose on a white background. It's set in a gold plated lace edged setting with an adjustable band, so it should fit most fingers.

The rose cab is approximately 19mm x 14mm.

name: Blue Frame with Lady with Deer Brooch
description:
This pretty brooch is set in a light blue resin frame and features a raised resin dome print of a lady and a deer (possibly Bambi!). 

The frame is approximately 67mm long and 43mm wide. The picture is approximately 40mm x 30mm.

Pins at the back with a stainless steel pin.

name: Owl & Birdcage Antique Brass Necklace with Blue Flowers
description:
This whimsical necklace is on the prettiest antique brass bar chain and features an antique brass birdcage, a round resin charm with a picture of an owl and some lovely glass blue flowers and glass pearl.

The chain is approximately 48.5cm long.

The birdcage is approximately 20mm x 15mm.

The owl pendant is approximately 18mm in diameter.

name: Gold Necklace with Black Framed Owl Pendant
description:
This whimsical necklace is on a delicate round link gold plated chain and features a resin domed picture of an owl set in a black resin frame.

The frame is approximately 65mm x 40mm.

The chain is approximately 51.5cm long.

name: Silver Necklace with White Bow & Blue and White Ladies Dancing Cameo
description:
This necklace features the celebration of women! 

Hanging off a silver plated, long link chain is a pretty silver and white enamelled bow and a silver lace edged framed blue and white cameo with a raised print of 3 women dancing in a garden or forest. Pretty and feminine.

The chain is approximately 52.5cm long.

The cameo is approximately 40mm x 30mm and is acrylic.

name: Purple Filigree Ring with Cream Heart with Colorful Flowers
description:
This pretty ring is set on an adjustable lavender filigree band, so it should fit most fingers.

The focal piece of the ring is a vintage cream loveheart with pretty pink and purple flowers. The loveheart is approximately 20mm in diameter.

One of a kind!

name: Long Necklace with Cream Teacup Pendant, Gold Bow & Chain
description:
Pretty and ladylike.

This necklace has a lovely long gold plated bar and lamp bead chain. Hanging off the chain is a large gold plated mesh bow and a cream resin frame with a porcelain picture of a teacup with colourful flowers.

The chain is approximately 72 cm long.
The resin pendant frame is approximately 50mm x 38mm.

name: Silver Necklace with Bunny in Forrest Pendant with Bow and Red Flower
description:
This sweet bunny necklace is on a silver plated ballchain and has a resin mint green bow with a glass coral swirl flower.

The pendant features a picture of a bunny in a forest in a silver plated frame and is approximately 35mm x 28mm.

The chain is approximately 51cm long.

If you have any further questions, please feel free to ask :)

name: Grey Frame with White Owl & Rhinestone Eyes Necklace
description:
This necklace has a dark gunmetal coloured chain and features a grey resin frame with a white resin owl with sparkling rhinestone eyes.

The frame is approximately 55mm wide and 45mm high.

The necklace is approximately 53cm long.

name: Sweetheart Rings
description:
My most favourite candy of all time have been made into rings!

This sweet rings are identical to the sweetheart lollies with cute sayings, except you can't eat them!  They are acrylic and are on silver plated adjustable ring bases, so they fit most fingers. 

They come in a variety of sayings!

name: Antique Silver Tapestry Floral Earrings
description:
These delightful earrings feature a floral cab with a tapestry effect in an antique silver setting. Earring hinges in the back.

The earring is approximately 30mm in length from the top of the earwire to the bottom of the earring and approximately 15mm at it's widest point.

name: Cream Large Resin Ring with Bee
description:
Cream resin ring with a black print of bee.

Cream resin ring is a size 6-7 

One of a kind.

name: Antique Brass Butterfuly Locket Watch
description:
This antique brass locket watch is on a long thick antique brass chain and features a butterfly on the front that spins around. If you press the button on the top, the face flicks open to reveal the watch face. Hanging at the bottom of the chain is a brass little butterfly too!

The locket is approximately 65mm x 45mm.

The chain is approximately 84cm long.

name: Long Gold Necklace with German Floral Cab in Black Frame and Gold Heart
description:
This lovely long gold plated necklace features a black enamel metal frame with a floral West German cab with flowers inside.  Hanging off the frame is a gold puffy loveheart.

The chain is a chunky long rectangular linked chain that is approximately 81cm long.

The frame is approximately 44mm x 37mm.

name: Cream Rose and Leaves with White Beads and Brass Chain Necklace
description:
This ladylike necklace features a cream acrylic rose with green leaves on a long antique brass plated chain with some vintage white glass beads along the bottom of the chain.

* The rose is approximately 40mm x 45mm. 
* The chain is approximately 103cm in length and are long rectangular links. 
* The white beads are vintage glass.

name: Mint Green Rose with White Beads and Brass Chain Necklace
description:
This ladylike necklace features a mint green acrylic rose on a long antique brass plated chain with some vintage white glass beads along the bottom of the chain.

* The rose is approximately 40mm x 45mm.
* The chain is approximately 103cm in length and are long rectangular links.
* The white beads are vintage glass.

name: Brass My Little Pony in White Frame Necklace
description:
For the kid in us all.............

This delightful and cheerful necklace features a cute picture of a man on a horse.  It kinda looks like a gingerbread man, and it kinda looks like My Little Pony.  You decide!  Either way, it's very colorful.

Set in a white resin frame that is approximately 50mm x 40mm, it's topped off with an antique brass mesh bow.  With a string of vintage white glass beads on either side and a decorate antique brass chain, it's about 70cm in length.

name: Black Resin Ring with Pink Rose
description:
This black ring is made from resin and features a pretty pink resin rose in the centre.

The ring size is approximately a US size 7-8 with a circumference of approximately 54.5mm.

name: Dusty Rose with Black Beads and Gold Chain Necklace
description:
This ladylike necklace features a lovely dusty dark pink acrylic rose on a long gold plated chain with some black czech glass beads along the bottom of the chain.

* The rose is approximately 40mm in diameter.
* The chain is approximately 87mm in length.
* Black beads are faceted czech glass.

name: Cream & Brown Marie Antoinette Rose & Stones Bracelet
description:
Vintage inspired!

This delightful bracelet is gold plated and features a Marie Antoinette charm which is approximately 30mm in diameter.  Surrounded by a cream resin rose and a couple of lovely opalesque glass stones, this bracelet is approximately 19.5cm in length.

name: Black and White Celtic Cross with Bird Brooch
description:
This dark but sweet brooch is made from resin and features a picture of a black bird on a celtic cross, captured in a black ornate frame.

The brooch is approximately 50mm x 40mm.

name: Silver Keep Calm & Carry On Locket
description:
This long hanging locket is on a silver plated chain and features a large silver plated locket measuring approximately 50mm x 40mm.  The centrepiece is a handmade cab made from porcelain which says "Keep Calm & Carry On"

The locket opens up and is fully functional.

name: White Wooden Bow Necklace
description:
This pretty little bow necklace is made from wood and is on a silver plated chain.

The bow is approximately 55mm wide and 40mm tall, with little polka dots and is white in color.

The chain is a long drawn link and is approximately 50cm.

name: Blue Wooden Bow Necklace
description:
This pretty little bow necklace is made from wood and is on a silver plated chain.

The bow is approximately 55mm wide and 40mm tall, with little polka dots and is blue in color.

The chain is a long drawn link and is approximately 50cm.

name: Yellow Wooden Bow Necklace
description:
This pretty little bow necklace is made from wood and is on a silver plated chain.

The bow is approximately 55mm wide and 40mm tall, with little polka dots and a bright yellow color.

The chain is a long drawn link and is approximately 50cm.

name: Round Floral Limogue Ring
description:
This pretty and vintage inspired ring is set on an adjustable ring base, so should fit most fingers.

With an antique silver frame, the centrepiece is a lovely vintage West German floral cab which is approximately 25mm in diameter.

name: Blue Statement Ring with Lovehearts
description:
Big and bold!

This ring is fully adjustable and features red and colorful lovehearts set in a light blue enamelled filigree setting.

The setting is approximately 40mmx37mm and has a resin cab in the centre.

name: Yellow Lovely Lady Hairpin
description:
Oh so ladylike!

This hairpin is lazercut from wood and features a picture of a lady with her hair in a bun, surrounded by pink flowers. The edge of the piece is black and white with a lovely black and white silk ribbon and silk flower centre up top. It's approximately 40mmx26mm. Set on a black hairpin.

name: Antique Brass Ring with Blue Butterfly and Pink and Yellow Flowers
description:
A delightful, fully adjustable antique brass ring.

The ring has a filigree base and has lovely resin pink and yellow roses around the edge with a cute blue butterfly centre. The centrepiece is approximately 20mm in diameter.

Being adjustable, it should fit most fingers.

name: The Curious Owl Necklace
description:
This owl is definitely curious, with those sparkling eyes!

This necklace is an antique brass color and features the face of an owl with large faceted opaque eyes.

The owl charm is approximately 55mm wide and 45mm tall. It hangs off a matching chain that is approximately 40cm long with an extention chain, so you can make it a few centermeters longer if you desire. You can see how it sits in the picture on the mannequin.
